<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天不愧是復活節，<delay20 />
果然相當熱鬧啊。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也是啦，<delay8 />過節就應該要開開心心的。<delay frames="40" />
連我<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也覺得特別開心咧？<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然看起來跟平常沒兩樣啦，<tag a="110" b="6" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00">今天是復活節，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以<colour id="3" />蹦蹦<colour id="65535" />來到廣場上了，對吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽說<delay8 />他好像提前把蛋啊、<delay8 />方程式啊，<delay8 />
都藏在島上了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那傢伙還真認真啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你<delay8 />還有閒工夫來我家啊，<delay20 />
不用去收集蛋嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再繼續磨蹭下去，就要被其他人搶先了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然話是這麼說，<delay8 />但是在島上
為了收集蛋四處奔波，<delay20 />感覺骨頭都要斷了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是蛋能直接到我家來，<delay8 />
就太感謝了，<delay20 /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊哈哈！</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />復活節就快到了。<delay frames="40" />
那一天，整座島都會充滿著蛋<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了，<delay8 /><colour id="3" />陸德里<colour id="65535" />跟我說過一件事。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是啊，<delay8 />使用哩數旅行券旅行的時候，<delay20 />
他在那座島上，
看到岩石旁邊有蛋喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，以那傢伙的個性來說，<delay8 />
說不定是太餓了，<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才會把石頭看成了蛋。<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是你有興趣，也可以去看看喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />復活節就快到了。<delay frames="40" />
那一天，整座島都會充滿著蛋<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了，<delay8 />我小時候聽過一個傳聞。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是啊，<delay8 />世界上有一種奇怪的椰子樹，<delay8 />
只要敲擊它<delay8 />
就會生出蛋耶。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是這座島也有椰子樹的話，<delay8 />
倒是滿值得一試的。<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說不定這傳聞是真的，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">那個，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你知道今年的復活節<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是<tag a="90" b="35" arg="0xcd00" />月<tag a="90" b="36" arg="0xcd00" />日吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你好好記住了嗎？<delay frames="40" />
因為復活節<delay8 />可是能夠吃到很多蛋的
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />重要節日啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><size value="75" />咦，<delay8 />不是嗎<tag a="110" b="0" />？<delay frames="60" /><size value="100" />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />算了，<delay8 />反正都是值得慶祝就對了！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不要在意這種小事啦！<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />哇哈哈！</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">對了，<delay8 />你聽說了嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />釣魚卻釣到蛋這件事！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />難不成是因為復活節快到了？<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />順帶一提，據說那傢伙瞄準的是<delay8 />
中型尺寸的魚影。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也來試看看，怎麼樣？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
